Scroller 18

Our last report is going to visualize with Scroller meaning the data gets visualized as an animating scrolling text.

Steps for this report

1. Drag and drop scroller from visualizations. If we are not able to find it from the listed visualizations, click on the ellipsis and

get more visuals from there.

2. Drag and drop

  • State column from COVID-19 in US table to category in fields box
  • Mortality rate from measure table to measure absolute in fields box

3. Scroller 

  • Auto size font - off
  • Font size - 20
  • Scroller speed - 1.2
  • Text color - #f9bba9, theme color 8, 60% lighter
  • Back ground color - Black 20 % lighter

4. Title - Off

5. Back ground - On

  • Color - Black, 20 % lighter

6. Boarder - on

  • Color - Black, 40% lighter


N.B. Lets make all the deaths same data label color - #f9bba9, theme color 8, 60% lighter
